name: Kimono
info: Yomi's kimono. Her favourite outfit in her wardrobe.

name: Pink Bikini
info: A pink, checkered bikini.

name: Black Bikini
info: A black bikini with white frills.

name: Swimsuit
info: A tight fitting outfit made from special materials. Enables streamlined movement through water.

name: School Swimsuit
info: A swimsuit which is designed with modesty in mind. Said to be worn by students in a foreign land.

name: Bunny Suit
info: A cotton tail and droopy, fake ears compliment this skin tight outfit.

name: French Maid
info: This outfit is said to be worn by servants of a civilisation to the west.

name: Wedding Dress
info: A white dress worn on a bride's special day. This particular dress has been designed to Isabella's own preferences.

name: Ribbons
info: One of the most mundane yet creatively designed outfits in Yomi's wardrobe, these ribbons have to be carefully placed.

name: Bondage
info: An outfit made of shiny, black material which rubs up against the skin.

name: Chocolate
info: A coating of chocolate which sustains itself with the user's mana. Said to be especially delicious.

name: Tiger Costume
info: Despite the name, this outfit was made from cotton and does not actually use any tiger-based materials.

name: Tribal Costume
info: Leather and fur are what ancient humans wore in the distant past. Some things never go out of style.

name: Space Suit
info: Forged from the mysterious material known as 'carbon fibre', this outfit provides exceptional protection.

name: Talisman
